{"tid":1540081,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我支持同政府妥協 你們可以打我了","createTime":"2019-09-04T10:49:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T11:15:07.000Z","uid":102775,"like":27,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"56d8fdcbe798a244af9552782934a5a360aea6aa","tid":1540081,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:49:12.000Z","msg":"邊個同政府妥協 我真係要打撚醒你<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要記得為我地犧牲嘅手足 仲有無數受傷被補嘅義士啊<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">五大訴求 缺一不可</span></span></strong><br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">光復香港 時代革命</span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"1cf2cc7ee42f7930ff218a8ddaf32f36ff262e8a","tid":1540081,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:50:16.000Z","msg":"自推十連1"},{"pid":"0f93f8c99498ada31bd15d11853b0a387bb78cba","tid":1540081,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:50:27.000Z","msg":"自推十連2"},{"pid":"b8ccd17bec475048d944f05dfd75dda0d7b73cf9","tid":1540081,"uid":290815,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T10:50:43.000Z","msg":"大家要到幾時先察覺，靠政府去實現五大訴求已經變成一個好恐怖既局？<br />\n<br />\n[時光倒流Re-post] 香港民權抗爭&mdash;&mdash;五大訴求，缺一不可？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1538204\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1538204</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n首先大家可以選擇服用咗以上文章先<br />\n<br />\n然後我可以反問一句，有冇人諗過五大訴求真係實現既情況會係點？<br />\n<br />\n係，的確可能證實到瘋狂既民意係可以改變到政府所作出既決定，但下次兩地一檢呢？再下次智慧燈柱、全面普教中呢？反送中2.0、3.0發生，真係好？點解要跟住個垃圾政權條尾走？<br />\n<br />\n香港人，唔好再「<span style=\"color: red;\">要求</span>」政府畀到五個願望你哋，請大家一齊親手達成依五個，甚至一百個願望都得，可唔可以？<br />\n<br />\n睇唔明我講咩既話請讀上面篇文章一次<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9938250a6866e34a5051e684a95c29e9c3e8c73b","tid":1540081,"uid":102775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"